description: Every single Pokemon in Pokemon Go has an elemental type. Types are categories a Pokemon is placed in these can determine a lot about a Pokemon. Pokemon Go Types can determine the strength and weakness of specific Pokemon. The most important thing is choosing the right type of pokemon can help you win the gym fight easily.
exampleInteractions: Alexa ask Poke Go Gym Helper how to beat a Pikachu
Tell me how to beat a Dragonite
What do I need to beat a Snorlax
name: Poke Go Gym Helper
shortDescription: Poke Go Gym Helper determines the type of any given pokemon and strength/weakness it fights against.
